694
00:36:31,910 --> 00:36:34,170
你需要我的帮助
Now, you need my help.

695
00:36:35,520 --> 00:36:36,600
今晚晚些时候
Later tonight,

696
00:36:37,810 --> 00:36:40,910
我要眼看着你签署
I'm going to watch you sign that bill

